      "solution": "import math\nx = str(input()) #'0.1231231232'\ni = 1\nwhile x[i] !='.':\n    ''' Recherche partie décimale '''\n    i = i+1\nl2 = []\nL2 = ''\na = 0\nh = 1\nwhile a == 0:\n    \n    ''' Recherche période répétée L2 '''\n    for j in range(i + h, len(x)):\n        #print(x[j])\n         \n        if x[j] not in L2:\n            L2 = L2 + x[j]\n        else:  \n            break\n    \n    periode =  x[i + h:].count(L2)\n    tailleDeci =  (len(x) -i + h - 2) \n    #print(L2, periode , len(L2) ,  tailleDeci )\n\n    reste = tailleDeci % periode\n    taille2 = tailleDeci - reste\n    if taille2 == periode * len(L2) : \n        a = a + 1\n    else:\n        h = h + 1\n        L2 = ''\n\nif a == 1:\n    \n    \"\"\"\"Calcul de la fraction de la période\"\"\"    \n    m = int(L2)\n    n = len(L2)\n    w=int('9'*(n))\n    numerateur = m//math.gcd(m,w)\n    denominateur = w//math.gcd(m,w)*10 ** (h-1)\n    partiP = int(float(x[:len(x)-tailleDeci+h])*10**(h-1))\n    DenoP = 10**(h-1)\n    ''' Mise au même dénominateur'''\n    Num2 = partiP * denominateur+ numerateur*DenoP\n    Den2 =  denominateur *DenoP\n    Num3 =  Num2//math.gcd(Num2,Den2 )\n    Den3 =Den2 //math.gcd(Num2,Den2 )\n    \n    \n    if Den3 == 1:\n        print(Num3)\n    else:\n        print(Num3,'/',Den3)\nelse: \n    print(int(x))",
